OL,5,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FPolice enter a 'house of horrors'
OL,7,     Fseeking a man on the run. Plus, an
OL,8,     Fepic 45-mile pursuit.
OL,9,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,10,     FDoors get smashed in dawn raids on
OL,11,     Fdrug dealers, shots are fired in a
OL,12,     Fsuburban siege, and bad guys are
OL,13,     Fchased at more than 100mph.
OL,14,G1700 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,15,     FUndercover detective Steve tails
OL,16,     Ftwo suspects who previously evaded
OL,17,     Fcapture, and later deals with a
OL,18,     Fwoman suspected of stealing
OL,19,     Fthousands of pounds' worth of
OL,20,     Fperfume. (Ep3)
