OL,5,G2000 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FIn Birmingham, Jane is fed up with
OL,7,     Fa painful rash on her scalp;
OL,8,     FMyfanwy has concerns that her mum
OL,9,     Fmay have sepsis after a procedure;
OL,10,     Fand Jean discusses her mental
OL,11,     Fhealth struggles.
OL,12,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FAfter a woman suffers cardiac
OL,14,     Farrest while driving, paramedics
OL,15,     Fmust induce a coma at the roadside
OL,16,     Fto save her. Meanwhile, a
OL,17,     F19-year-old suffers critical
OL,18,     Finjuries in a motorcycle crash.
