OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FParamedics rush to help a
OL,7,     F67-year-old HGV driver who has
OL,8,     Fsuffered a cardiac arrest, and, in
OL,9,     FHillingdon, a man who has suffered
OL,10,     Fsevere burns after lighting a
OL,11,     Fbonfire with petrol.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Dev Shah treats a Nottingham
OL,14,     FForest fan with a large head cyst,
OL,15,     Fand Dr Toby Nelson deals with a
OL,16,     Fseries of mini lipomas that look
OL,17,     Flike a string of pearls.
